<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV13">
<l>taṉivaḷar ceṅkō ṉaṭāvu taḻalvā yaracaviyap</l>
<l>paṉivaḷar ceṅkō liruḷvīṟ ṟiruntatu pārmuḻutun</l>
<l>tuṉivaḷar kātaṟ ṟuḻāyait tuḻāvutaṇ vāṭaitaṭin</l>
<l>tiṉivaḷai kāppava rāreṉai yūḻika ḷīrvaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the reign of [him with] fiery mouth, ends, who wields [his] solitude-growing red sceptre,</l>
<l>darkness with dew-growing just sceptre sits enthroned on the whole earth.</l>
<l>Who will now guard [my] bangles, cutting down the cool north wind</l>
<l>that stirs the Tulsi of love that grows hatred? Aeons saw at me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
